'''前扣带皮层'''（英文：Anterior cingulate cortex），在[[人腦|人脑]]中，是[[大脑|大脑]][[扣带皮层|扣带皮层]]的前部，包围了[[胼胝体|胼胝体]]的前部<ref name=":6" />。前扣带皮层属于[[布罗德曼分区系统|布罗德曼分区系统]]第24、25、32、33分区<ref name=":6">{{Cite book|chapter=Neuroanatomy, Cingulate Cortex|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK537077/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=30725762|first=Fareed R.|last=Jumah|first2=Rimal H.|last2=Dossani|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210221509/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK537077/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。前扣带皮层参与了许多脑部的高阶功能，包括[[注意力|注意力]]分配<ref name=":0">{{cite journal|title=The anterior cingulate cortex mediates processing selection in the Stroop attentional conflict paradigm|date=January 1990|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|issue=1|doi=10.1073/pnas.87.1.256|volume=87|pages=256–9|bibcode=1990PNAS...87..256P|pmc=53241|pmid=2296583|vauthors=Pardo JV, Pardo PJ, Janer KW, Raichle ME}}</ref>、奖励、[[决策|决策]]<ref name="Bush02">{{cite journal|title=Dorsal anterior cingulate cortex: a role in reward-based decision making|date=January 2002|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|issue=1|doi=10.1073/pnas.012470999|volume=99|pages=523–8|bibcode=2002PNAS...99..523B|pmc=117593|pmid=11756669|vauthors=Bush G, Vogt BA, Holmes J, Dale AM, Greve D, Jenike MA, Rosen BR}}</ref>、[[道德|道德]]及[[伦理学|伦理]]<ref name=":1">{{cite journal|title=Salience network engagement with the detection of morally laden information|date=July 2017|journal=Social Cognitive and Affective Neuroscience|issue=7|doi=10.1093/scan/nsx035|volume=12|pages=1118–1127|pmc=5490682|pmid=28338944|vauthors=Sevinc G, Gurvit H, Spreng RN}}</ref>、冲动控制（譬如[[错误检测与纠正|错误检测与纠正]]）<ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=In need of constraint: Understanding the role of the cingulate cortex in the impulsive mind|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27989844/|last=Golchert|first=Johannes|last2=Smallwood|first2=Jonathan|date=2017-02-01|journal=NeuroImage|doi=10.1016/j.neuroimage.2016.10.041|volume=146|pages=804–813|issn=1095-9572|pmid=27989844|last3=Jefferies|first3=Elizabeth|last4=Liem|first4=Franziskus|last5=Huntenburg|first5=Julia M.|last6=Falkiewicz|first6=Marcel|last7=Lauckner|first7=Mark E.|last8=Oligschläger|first8=Sabine|last9=Villringer|first9=Arno}}</ref>、情感<ref name=":3">{{cite journal|title=The functional architecture of human empathy|date=June 2004|journal=Behavioral and Cognitive Neuroscience Reviews|issue=2|doi=10.1177/1534582304267187|volume=3|pages=71–100|pmid=15537986|vauthors=Decety J, Jackson PL}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title=Empathy examined through the neural mechanisms involved in imagining how I feel versus how you feel pain|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16140345/|last=Jackson|first=Philip L.|last2=Brunet|first2=Eric|date=2006|journal=Neuropsychologia|issue=5|doi=10.1016/j.neuropsychologia.2005.07.015|volume=44|pages=752–761|issn=0028-3932|pmid=16140345|last3=Meltzoff|first3=Andrew N.|last4=Decety|first4=Jean|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525175038/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16140345/|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。

== 结构 ==
{{参见|扣带皮层}}
在解剖学上，前扣带皮层位于[[后扣带皮层|后扣带皮层]]前部，可分为背部（认知区）、前部（情感区）<ref name=":5">{{Cite journal|title=Cognitive and emotional influences in anterior cingulate cortex|url=https://www.cell.com/trends/cognitive-sciences/abstract/S1364-6613(00)01483-2|last=Bush|first=George|last2=Luu|first2=Phan|date=2000-06-01|journal=Trends in Cognitive Sciences|issue=6|doi=10.1016/S1364-6613(00)01483-2|volume=4|pages=215–222|language=En|issn=1364-6613|pmid=10827444|last3=Posner|first3=Michael I.|last4=Bush|first4=George|last5=Luu|first5=Phan|last6=Posner|first6=Michael I.|last7=Bush|first7=George|last8=Luu|first8=Phan|last9=Posner|first9=Michael I.|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2013-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131011090443/http://www.cell.com/trends/cognitive-sciences/abstract/S1364-6613(00)01483-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。背部常被称为“中扣带皮层（midcingulate cortex）”，与[[前额叶皮质|前额叶皮质]]、[[顶叶|顶叶]]、[[运动系统|运动系统]]等区域相连，使其成为“[[自上而下和自下而上設計|自上而下和自下而上刺激]]”的核心站<ref name=":6" /><ref name="Posner98">{{cite book|vauthors=Posner MI, DiGirolamo GJ|chapter=Executive attention: Conflict, target detection, and cognitive control|editor=Parasuraman R|title=The attentive brain|publisher=MIT Press|location=Cambridge, Mass|year=1998|isbn=0-262-16172-9}}</ref>。前部则与[[杏仁核|杏仁核]]、[[伏隔核|伏隔核]]、[[下丘脑|下丘脑]]、[[丘脑|丘脑]]、前[[岛叶|岛叶]]等相连，参与评估情感显化和激励性信息<ref name="Posner98" />。

特别的是，前扣带皮层含有[[纺锤体神经元|纺锤体神经元]]（仅在人类及其它[[灵长类动物|灵长类动物]]、[[大象|大象]]、[[鯨豚類|鲸豚类]]动物上发现），与脑部处理困难问题的功能有关<ref>{{Cite web|title=Brain Cells for Socializing|url=https://www.smithsonianmag.com/science-nature/brain-cells-for-socializing-133855450/|accessdate=2021-04-04|work=Smithsonian Magazine|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323161204/https://www.smithsonianmag.com/science-nature/brain-cells-for-socializing-133855450/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=The anterior cingulate cortex. The evolution of an interface between emotion and cognition|date=May 2001|journal=Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences|doi=10.1111/j.1749-6632.2001.tb03476.x|volume=935|pages=107–17|bibcode=2001NYASA.935..107A|pmid=11411161|vauthors=Allman JM, Hakeem A, Erwin JM, Nimchinsky E, Hof P}}</ref>。

== 功能 ==
许多研究认为，前扣带皮层参与了[[错误检测与纠正|错误检测与纠正]]、任务预期、激励、注意力、情感调控等功能<ref name=":0" /><ref name="Bush02" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" />。在压力环境下，前扣带皮层可能还参与调节[[自主神经系统|自主神经系统]]，譬如调节血压和心率<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Anterior cingulate activity correlates with blood pressure during stress|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2246096/|last=Gianaros|first=Peter J.|last2=Derbyshire|first2=Stuart W. G.|date=2005-11|journal=Psychophysiology|issue=6|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8986.2005.00366.x|volume=42|pages=627–635|issn=0048-5772|pmc=2246096|pmid=16364058|last3=May|first3=J. Christopher|last4=Siegle|first4=Greg J.|last5=Gamalo|first5=Mark A.|last6=Jennings|first6=J. Richard|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308211656/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2246096/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 临床 ==
前扣带皮层异常可能与[[强迫症|强迫症]]、情绪不稳、无法认知错误、{{le|无动性缄默症|Akinetic mutism}}、[[社交焦慮|社交焦虑]]等病症有关<ref name=":5" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Role of the dorsal anterior cingulate cortex in obsessive-compulsive disorder: converging evidence from cognitive neuroscience and psychiatric neurosurgery|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27035167/#:~:text=One%20of%20the%20core%20dysfunctions,anterior%20cingulate%20cortex%20(dACC).&text=CONCLUSIONS%20Although%20abnormalities%20in%20brain,dACC%20plays%20a%20central%20role.|last=McGovern|first=Robert A.|last2=Sheth|first2=Sameer A.|date=2017-01|journal=Journal of Neurosurgery|issue=1|doi=10.3171/2016.1.JNS15601|volume=126|pages=132–147|issn=1933-0693|pmid=27035167|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022418/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27035167/#:~:text=One%20of%20the%20core%20dysfunctions,anterior%20cingulate%20cortex%20(dACC).&text=CONCLUSIONS%20Although%20abnormalities%20in%20brain,dACC%20plays%20a%20central%20role.|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Pains and Pleasures of Social Life|url=https://science.sciencemag.org/content/323/5916/890|last=Lieberman|first=Matthew D.|last2=Eisenberger|first2=Naomi I.|date=2009-02-13|journal=Science|issue=5916|doi=10.1126/science.1170008|volume=323|pages=890–891|language=en|issn=0036-8075|pmid=19213907|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516154901/https://science.sciencemag.org/content/323/5916/890|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

